<sect2 id='gimp-prefs-new-image' lang="de;en;fr;zh_CN">
  <title lang='en'>New Image Preferences</title>
  <title lang='de'>Neues Bild</title>
  <title lang='fr'>Nouvelle image</title>
  <title lang="zh_CN">新建图形</title>

  <indexterm lang='en'>
    <primary>dialogs</primary>
    <secondary>preferences</secondary>
    <tertiary>new image</tertiary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang='de'>
    <primary>Dialoge</primary>
    <secondary>Einstellungen</secondary>
    <tertiary>Neues Bild</tertiary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang='fr'>
    <primary>Dialogue</primary>
    <secondary>Préférences</secondary>
    <tertiary>Nouvelle image</tertiary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="zh_CN">
    <primary>对话框</primary>
    <secondary>首选项</secondary>
    <tertiary>新建图像</tertiary>
  </indexterm>

  <informalfigure>  
    <mediaobject>
      <imageobject role='html'>
        <imagedata fileref='../images/preferences/prefs-new-image.png'
        format="PNG" lang='en;zh_CN'/>
        <imagedata
        fileref='../images/preferences/de/prefs-new-image.png'
        format="PNG" lang='de'/>
        <imagedata
        fileref='../images/preferences/fr/prefs-new-image.png'
        format="PNG" lang='fr'/>
      </imageobject>
      <imageobject role='tex'>
        <imagedata fileref='../images/preferences/prefs-new-image.png'
        format="PNG" lang='en;zh_CN' width='14cm' scalefit='1' />
        <imagedata
        fileref='../images/preferences/de/prefs-new-image.png'
        format="PNG" lang='de' width='14cm' scalefit='1' />
        <imagedata
        fileref='../images/preferences/fr/prefs-new-image.png'
        format="PNG" lang='fr' width='14cm' scalefit='1'/>
      </imageobject>

      <caption>
        <para lang='en'>
          New Image Preferences
        </para>
        <para lang='fr'>
          Préférences de Nouvelle Image
        </para>
        <para lang="zh_CN">
          新建图形首选项
        </para>
      </caption>
    </mediaobject>
  </informalfigure>

  <para lang='de'>
    Verändern Sie Standardeinstellungen des Dialogs zum <link
    linkend='gimp-file-new'>Erstellen eines neuen Bildes</link>.
  </para>
  <para lang='en'>
    This tab lets you customize the default settings for the New Image
    dialog.  See the <link
    linkend='gimp-file-new'>New Image Dialog</link> section
    for an explanation of what each of the values means.
  </para>
  <para lang='fr'>
    Modification des valeurs par défaut du dialogue Nouvelle image.
    Les explications de chaque paramètre sont dans la partie
    <link linkend='gimp-file-new'>Dialogue Nouvelle image</link>.
  </para>
  <para lang="zh_CN">
    您可以在该页定制新建图形对话框的默认设置。各个值的含义请看<link linkend='gimp-file-new'>新建图形对话框</link>。
  </para>


</sect2>
